      "text": "I'm not"
    },
    {
      "start": 800.36,
      "end": 801.86,
      "text": "어, 전 그런 적 없는데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 801.86,
      "end": 802.24,
      "text": "아닌데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 802.76,
      "end": 803.14,
      "text": "라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 803.14,
      "end": 805.24,
      "text": "네, 억울하다는 듯이 표현을 했죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 805.24,
      "end": 806.34,
      "text": "She's denying it"
    },
    {
      "start": 806.34,
      "end": 807.86,
      "text": "I think she is holding back"
    },
    {
      "start": 807.86,
      "end": 809.48,
      "text": "어허, 맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 809.48,
      "end": 810.16,
      "text": "그렇지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 810.16,
      "end": 811.84,
      "text": "지금은 조금"
    },
    {
      "start": 811.84,
      "end": 813.66,
      "text": "She must have been embarrassed"
    },
    {
      "start": 813.66,
      "end": 814.36,
      "text": "a little bit"
    },
    {
      "start": 814.36,
      "end": 814.94,
      "text": "at first"
    },
    {
      "start": 814.94,
      "end": 815.44,
      "text": "하지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 815.44,
      "end": 817.98,
      "text": "이제 곧 괜찮아지지 않을까"
    },
    {
      "start": 817.98,
      "end": 819.46,
      "text": "극복할 수 있지 않을까"
    },
    {
      "start": 819.46,
      "end": 820.34,
      "text": "예상이 됩니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 820.34,
      "end": 821.42,
      "text": "She also has a lot"
    },
    {
      "start": 821.42,
      "end": 822.22,
      "text": "on her mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 822.22,
      "end": 822.54,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 822.54,
      "end": 823.64,
      "text": "Her family's business"
    },
    {
      "start": 823.64,
      "end": 824.0,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 824.0,
      "end": 824.98,
      "text": "Helping her family"
    },
    {
      "start": 824.98,
      "end": 825.42,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 825.42,
      "end": 827.4,
      "text": "So she needs to forget about that"
    },
    {
      "start": 827.4,
      "end": 828.72,
      "text": "and let loose"
    },
    {
      "start": 828.72,
      "end": 830.82,
      "text": "날아올랐으면 좋겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 830.82,
      "end": 831.72,
      "text": "Fly"
    },
    {
      "start": 831.72,
      "end": 832.74,
      "text": "네, 마지막으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 832.74,
      "end": 833.72,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 833.72,
      "end": 835.48,
      "text": "Ruby, no"
    },
    {
      "start": 835.48,
      "end": 836.7,
      "text": "If you're going to pick"
    },
    {
      "start": 836.7,
      "end": 837.24,
      "text": "Joanie Mitchell"
    },
    {
      "start": 837.24,
      "end": 838.38,
      "text": "you're going to sing it"
    },
    {
      "start": 838.38,
      "end": 839.62,
      "text": "This is one of the great songs"
    },
    {
      "start": 839.62,
      "end": 840.44,
      "text": "Yeah, I know"
    },
    {
      "start": 840.44,
      "end": 842.79,
      "text": "You either find a way to connect to it"
    },
    {
      "start": 842.79,
      "end": 843.95,
      "text": "or pick a different song"
    },
    {
      "start": 843.95,
      "end": 845.07,
      "text": "Okay, come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 845.07,
      "end": 845.89,
      "text": "Shake your body"
    },
    {
      "start": 845.89,
      "end": 846.59,
      "text": "Shake it"
    },
    {
      "start": 846.59,
      "end": 847.23,
      "text": "Shake your arms"
    },
    {
      "start": 847.23,
      "end": 848.01,
      "text": "Come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 848.01,
      "end": 851.01,
      "text": "Now, sing back at me"
    },
    {
      "start": 851.01,
      "end": 852.73,
      "text": "Me, me, me, me"
    },
    {
      "start": 852.73,
      "end": 855.39,
      "text": "Come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 855.39,
      "end": 857.59,
      "text": "Me, me, me, me"
    },
    {
      "start": 857.59,
      "end": 859.39,
      "text": "No, no, you're holding it"
    },
    {
      "start": 859.39,
      "end": 860.07,
      "text": "I'm not"
    },
    {
      "start": 860.07,
      "end": 862.74,
      "text": "네, 이 미경님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 862.74,
      "end": 863.94,
      "text": "조크쌤"
    },
    {
      "start": 863.94,
      "end": 865.42,
      "text": "쿵짝이 잘 맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 865.42,
      "end": 866.0,
      "text": "쿡"
    },
    {
      "start": 866.0,
      "end": 866.82,
      "text": "쿡"
    },
    {
      "start": 866.82,
      "end": 869.32,
      "text": "Yeah, we work in perfect harmony"
    },
    {
      "start": 869.32,
      "end": 871.04,
      "text": "Perfect harmony"
    },
    {
      "start": 871.04,
      "end": 872.28,
      "text": "네, 참"
    },
    {
      "start": 872.28,
      "end": 873.56,
      "text": "쿵짝이 잘 맞아서"
    },
    {
      "start": 873.56,
      "end": 874.32,
      "text": "너무 감사합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 874.32,
      "end": 876.64,
      "text": "As long as we don't sing together"
    },
    {
      "start": 876.64,
      "end": 878.84,
      "text": "I really like our harmony"
    },
    {
      "start": 878.84,
      "end": 879.86,
      "text": "아, 참"
    },
    {
      "start": 879.86,
      "end": 881.14,
      "text": "노래도 잘하시잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 881.14,
      "end": 883.34,
      "text": "With all your heart"
    },
    {
      "start": 883.34,
      "end": 884.9,
      "text": "With my heart"
    },
    {
      "start": 884.9,
      "end": 885.4,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 885.4,
      "end": 887.08,
      "text": "I do put passion into it"
    },
    {
      "start": 887.08,
      "end": 888.2,
      "text": "Bad voice"
    },
    {
      "start": 888.2,
      "end": 889.1,
      "text": "But lots of passion"
    },
    {
      "start": 889.1,
      "end": 890.52,
      "text": "아, 참"
    },
    {
      "start": 890.52,
      "end": 892.44,
      "text": "우리 노래할 기회가 있을 때마다"
